knonws: Mom went to the shop. She got me a pet. The pet Mom got from the pet shop was a fox. But the fox got out of the box. Mom said not to be sad. She will find the fox. She took the box. Mom was gone for a long time. Now Mom is back. She did find the fox! The fox is in the box. Mom has to chop food for the fox. I can sit with the fox.
